[121,975]]},{"text":"中國文化大革命和法國革命中相似現象的共同社會基。","box":[[120,990],[734,991],[734,1011],[120,1010]]},{"text":"[1] Edward Berenson:“A Permanent Revolution: The Historiography of 1789,\"","box":[[115,1076],[737,1077],[737,1101],[115,1100]]},{"text":"ModernChina,Winter1995.","box":[[118,1104],[327,1105],[327,1125],[118,1124]]},{"text":"一12一","box":[[120,1168],[190,1168],[190,1186],[120,1186]]}],"dimensions":{"height":1241,"width":857}}